  "instructions": [
    "Heat lard or oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the chicken to the skillet and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the onion and garlic to the skillet and cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add cumin, chili powder, salt, and pepper to the skillet and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the chicken back to the skillet and stir to coat with the spice mixture.",
    "Cook for an additional 2-3 minutes, or until the chicken is cooked through.",
    "Warm tortillas by wrapping them in a damp paper towel and microwaving for 20-30 seconds.",
    "Assemble the tacos by placing a portion of the chicken mixture onto a tortilla and topping with avocado, sour cream, and any desired additional toppings.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
